sdb - stardict browser

use a good dict like
https://github.com/reader-dict/monolingual

Do not handle regexp, html
	because i dont use all these
	also im a unskilled programmer and have no enengy to do some stuff.
	(gumbo-parser is fine to work with thou)

supported:

- .syn
- .off: .idx, .syn offset cache
- case-insensitive search, latin1 accent folding, unicode case folding

# .oft spec revealed by sdcv's source code

30 "StarDict's Cache, Version: 0.2"| 4 0x51a4d1c1| n*4 offsets to pages starts
in machine endian

while n = 2+(wordcount-1)/ENTR_PER_PAGE, 2 for 0 and end byte.
ENTR_PER_PAGE = 32

i dont feel happy about its not including last word's offset but calcing runtime.

# .off spec

n*4 offsets to pages starts in index file
in machine endian

while n = 2+(wordcount-1)/ENTR_PER_PAGE, 2 for 0 and offset of last word
ENTR_PER_PAGE = 64

